  <title>Send files to a Bluetooth device</title>

  <p>You can send files from your computer to other Bluetooth compatible devices, like some mobile
  phones, some speakers, or other computers. You can send files in one of three
  ways: using the Bluetooth icon on the task bar, from the Bluetooth settings
  window, or directly from your Documents folder. Some types of devices don't allow the transfer
  of files, or specific types of files, so you may want to check with your device first.</p>

